GEBHARD, Anna Goble (37); 

feloniously attempting to kill and murder 




   Anne Elizabeth Goble Gebhard, with intent to murder her and to do her some grievous bodily harm.

Verdict, 


                     Guilty in all cases in the conspiracy counts; 


                     Not Guilty on counts charging false pretences.







EVERETT, James (42, carman);

 feloniously wounding 



   Agnes Davis, with intent to do her some grievous bodily harm.

BROMLEY HALL , master miller, Godstone, near Dorking;
WILLIAM KING . blacksmith, Ross Road, Dorking; and
JOSEPH HENRY SMITH . 303, Haydon Road, Wimbledon, were called as to Luck's character.
